videos.description: Remy Martin grabs the offensive board and passes outside to Shannon Evans II who knocks it in from behind the arc in the first half against Pacific.
videos.headline: ASU's Remy feeds Evans for 3

videos.description: Arizona State's Vitaliy Shibel steals and takes it to the rim for an easy slam in the first half against Pacific.
videos.headline: ASU's Shibel finishes nifty one-handed dunk

videos.description: Tra Holder misses a long 3-pointer but Mickey Mitchell grabs the rebound and slams it in with his right hand against Pacific.
videos.headline: ASU's Mitchell throws it down to start second half

videos.description: Shannon Evans II sends a tricky no-look pass to De'Quon Lake who jams it in against Pacific.
videos.headline: ASU's Evans sets up Lake's flush

videos.description: Remy Martin gets aggressive, grabs the defensive board and goes to-to-coast to find Mickey Mitchell who knocks in a layup in the second half.
videos.headline: Martin speeds and feeds for ASU

videos.description: Da'Quon Lake swats away a layup attempt inside the paint and Tra Holder gets it back for the Sun Devils before speeding for an easy layup in the second half.
videos.headline: ASU's Lake extends for block

videos.description: Remy Martin rises up and dishes to Austin Witherill who knocks in a sweet 3-pointer from the left wing at the end of the second half against Pacific.
videos.headline: ASU's Martin gets airborne to find Witherill for triple
